<!--this is a html snippet for an _image_.
It is used by a _card_ table to display an image.
It uses the following variables:
 - _image_source_ - The image to be displayed. For example, "image.jpg".
 - _height_
 - _width_
-->
<tr class="image_row">
<td class="image_entry" colspan="2">
<a class="image"><img src="{{{image_source}}}" width="{{{width}}}" height="{{{height}}}" /></a>
</td>
</tr>